# Database development (organization template)

> Document **ORM**, **schema folder**, and **migration commands** in **`AGENTS.md`**.

## Organization

- Prefer **one table/model per file** (or follow your existing house pattern consistently).
- Export tables, insert/update schemas, and inferred types as your codebase already does.

## Access

- Use the shared **`db`** (or equivalent) instance from your workspace package — avoid ad-hoc pools scattered across routes.

## Migrations

- Follow team policy for **push / migrate / generate**. Do not rewrite published migration history unless policy explicitly allows it.

## Queries

- Prefer the ORM query builder; reserve raw SQL for documented exceptions.
